pl.sql
Class PlTypes

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--pl.sql.PlTypes
public class PlTypes
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains constants for all types supported by the Persistence Layer. Each type has a corresponding get method in java.sql.ResultSet interface (except UNDEFINED).
